## 7. Ethical Statement & Platform Naming Source
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 7.1 Ethical Compliance
- BCI route: Only neural signal reading, no writing, no stimulation, no neural control, fully compliant with global neuroethical guidelines.
- No genomic editing, no nuclear invasion, no irreversible neural manipulation.
- All materials are biodegradable, no permanent residue in the body.

### 7.2 Platform Naming Source
- The platform name "ELEANOR" is derived from the game character Eleanor; the safety mechanism "KALTSIT Technology" is derived from the game character Kal'tsit (凯尔希), for scientific research naming only.

### 7.3 Global Collaboration
All researchers are welcome to carry out research based on the ELEANOR platform. All derivative works must attribute the original author Chenzhuo and cite this GitHub repository.
